AlphaEarth embeddings in this directory — provenance and attribution
====================================================================

These .npy files are a DERIVED product, not the original dataset. Each file is a
per-station 64-dimensional vector: the spatial MEAN of the
GOOGLE/SATELLITE_EMBEDDING/V1/ANNUAL image over a 100 m buffer around the DWD
station, sampled at scale 10 m, for each year 2020-2024.

  filename: {station_id}_{year}.npy   shape: (64,)   dtype: float32
  index.csv lists the extraction manifest.

Extraction code: scripts/03_extract_alphaearth.py and scripts/10_extract_added_embeddings.py

